      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im doing a paper for my anthro class and i wanted to get a better handle on some foundational concepts. can u help me explain the main ways that \"modern\" civilizations generally differ from what are traditionally called \"primitive\" social structures? like what are the key markers that show a shift from one to the other?",
